    "Postgraduate academic success in this study refers to success in the participants' research.",
    "ChatGPT is an artificial intelligence language model developed by OpenAI and is capable of generating human-like text (Baytak, 2024; Brown et al., 2020).",
    "As highlighted by Van Dis et al. (2023), ChatGPT plays a crucial role in assisting postgraduate students, especially master's students and doctoral candidates, in expediting their research processes and facilitating the retrieval of accurate information from previous studies for their research endeavours.",
    "Imran and Almusharraf (2023) assert that ChatGPT enhances students' productivity in research by offering advanced writing assistance.",
    "According to Dwivedi et al. (2023), ChatGPT has a significant impact particularly on the research component of higher education."
